==English==
===Etymology===
From [[w:Robert Burns|Robert '''Burns''']] + [[night]] 

===Noun phrase===
'''Burns' night'''
# held on the evening of 25th January in celebration of the [[Scottish]] [[poet]] '''Robert Burns'''. Burns was born on that day in 1759.

